  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A block-pushing puzzle game with original mechanics that combine in many interesting ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the fireworks next to the flames</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or use powder to connect them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some crates will need to be assembled first</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 hand-crafted levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited undo, redo and restarts</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear level progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 outfits (skins) to unlock</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A block-pushing puzzle game with original mechanics that combine in many interesting ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move the fireworks next to the flames</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/a1221296b0aea32ab02a9cf364fdec7e.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or use powder to connect them</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/166c499e8c209cebea9163e74d619854.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some crates will need to be assembled first</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.poster.avif?t=1761783626\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.webm?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359440/extras/c2a02ecf8202a7af55cbeeb61c1f4c7c.mp4?t=1761783626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 hand-crafted levels</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlimited undo, redo and restarts</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear level progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 outfits (skins) to unlock</p></li></ul>",
